# Secrets and env variable Patterns

## Overview

This rule defines how to properly handle secrets and env variables in Encore applications

## Code example

```typescript
// INCORRECT (what Cursor tries to do by default):
// process.env.SECRET_NAME

// CORRECT:
// Use Encore's built-in secrets mechanism
import { secret } from 'encore.dev/config';

// Example of proper secret usage in Encore:
const apiKey = secret('API_KEY')();
```
